# Phase 1 Generated Screens - Summary

## Overview

Successfully generated **8 critical Academic ERP screens** using Google Stitch MCP. All screens have `COMPLETE` status and are ready for React+Tailwind conversion.

**Project ID:** `5304011400071064164`  
**Total Generation Time:** ~35 minutes  
**Design System:** Inter font, Light mode, ROUND_EIGHT (8px border-radius), Saturation: 2

---

