## Design Consistency

All screens follow a unified design language:

| Element | Specification |
|---------|---------------|
| Font | Inter (from Google Fonts) |
| Border Radius | 8px (ROUND_EIGHT) for desktop, 12px (ROUND_TWELVE) for mobile |
| Color Mode | Light |
| Saturation | Medium (2/4) |
| Primary Colors | Blue (#0da2e7) for Admin, Amber (#f59f0a) for Teacher, Purple (#895af6) for Student |
| Header Pattern | Gradient (primary-to-darker) with title + subtitle |
| Cards | White bg, shadow-lg, border-l-4 accent |
| Tables | Alternating rows, sortable headers, action columns |
| Badges | Colored (green=success, yellow=warning, red=error, blue=info) |

---

## Next Steps

### Phase 3: Integration

1. **Download HTML files** (8 total, use URLs above)
2. **Convert to React components**:
   - Extract structure from HTML
   - Replace inline styles with Tailwind classes
   - Add TypeScript interfaces
   - Wire up API calls
3. **Add routes** to [AppRoutes.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/routes/AppRoutes.tsx):
   ```typescript
   // Admin routes
   <Route path="/admin/sessions" element={<AcademicSessions />} />
   <Route path="/admin/programs" element={<ProgramsCurriculum />} />
   <Route path="/admin/assignments" element={<TeacherAssignments />} />
   <Route path="/admin/exams" element={<ExamBuilder />} />
   <Route path="/admin/results" element={<ResultProcessing />} />
   <Route path="/admin/transcripts" element={<TranscriptGenerator />} />
   
   // Teacher routes
   <Route path="/teacher/marks" element={<MarksEntry />} />
   
   // Student routes
   <Route path="/student/results" element={<ReportCard />} />
   ```
4. **Test** with existing API endpoints
5. **Verify** build: `npm run build`

---

## API Mapping

Each screen maps to existing backend endpoints:

| Screen | Primary API Endpoints |
|--------|----------------------|
| Academic Sessions | `GET/POST /admin/academic/sessions` |
| Programs & Curriculum | `GET /admin/academic/programs`, `GET /admin/academic/programs/{id}` |
| Teacher Assignment | `POST /admin/academic/subjects/{id}/assign-teacher` |
| Exam Builder | `GET/POST /admin/exams` |
| Marks Entry | `POST /teacher/marks` |
| Result Processing | `POST /admin/exams/{id}/process-results` |
| Report Card | `GET /student/exams`, `GET /student/transcript` |
| Transcript Generator | `GET /admin/transcript/{studentId}` |

All endpoints are already implemented in [api/academic_endpoints.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/academic_endpoints.php) and [api/exam_endpoints.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/exam_endpoints.php).
